## Pre-Flight Security Analysis

### Install `recharts` charting library

| Check | Assessment |
|---|---|
| **Impact Analysis** | **Local** â€” adds a package to `node_modules/`. No system-wide changes. |
| **Security Threat Model** | Low risk. `recharts` is one of the most popular React charting libraries (23k+ GitHub stars, millions of weekly downloads). No known vulnerabilities. |
| **Sanity Check** | Native SVG/Canvas charts would avoid a dependency but would take significantly more code. Recharts is the standard solution. |

> **ACTION:** `npm install recharts`  
> **RATIONALE:** Needed for line charts, bar charts, donut/pie charts, and area charts.  
> **SECURITY RATING:** Low Risk  
> **UNDO ACTION:** `npm uninstall recharts`

